headline: Two Huge AI Winners In 2024 Have Room To Run, Analysts Say
summary: Coherent and GE Vernova, two artificial intellience plays, received positive analyst initiations on Wednesday. Coherent stock leaped to a new high. GE Vernova stock popped in buy range. The analysts rated the AI-related stocks, whose shares have already made huge moves in 2024, as buys.
